data.description: Beautiful well maintained 716 sq foot 1 bedroom, 1 bath home with an open concept living room & kitchen/dining combo, & a detached garage.   Property features wonderful large mature shade trees and a covered deck.   RV Parking with dump and 50 amp hook up for RV's.  Views in all directions and steps away from open desert and  and easy access to interstate 40.  Storage shed and fenced on three sides.
